{"tid":1222023,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【戰歌重填整合】Do you hear the people sing?","createTime":"2019-06-14T10:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T18:47:04.000Z","uid":154486,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"61a1692152c2f11eab16bb7fd92d411fbf026691","tid":1222023,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:43:24.000Z","msg":"歌聲裡燃亮赤<span style=\"color: blue;\">火</span><br />\n[red<span style=\"color: blue;\">]火</span>光已蔓延漸放茫[/red]<br />\n這血肉魂魄有天消散 依然唱和著戰歌<br />\n<br />\n歌聲裡熊亮似<span style=\"color: blue;\">火</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">火</span>光裡我無懼折磨<br />\n悲傷過後 讓我將往日壓迫踏破<br />\n<br />\n重重暗淡 叩首屈膝 雨打風吹遇太多<br />\n但抗爭這命裡職責 在心血液和脈搏<br />\n流血若河 困惑時 軟弱時 喊著戰歌！<br />\n<br />\n*副歌*<br />\n<br />\n如林盾陣 無懼戰士 覺醒披甲護這火<br />\n為這家發誓要抵抗 逆轉我命途沒錯<br />\n魂魄尚留 血在流 卻自由 唱著戰歌！<br />\n<br />\n*副歌*<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n紅色係巴打提議<br />\n<br />\n因為想大家識唱，所以盡量押韻<br />\n另外副歌句尾接句首個火字想留番，個flow會好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21be61047aa73235b86f1c192cdef6251c5ff9a3","tid":1222023,"uid":43041,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:43:12.000Z","msg":"原歌霸氣好多。<br />\n<br />\n不過都好過&ldquo;問誰未發聲&rdquo;既，聽到毛管凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ac127fbaa8a58740c02b12404b097163adc98e","tid":1222023,"uid":207942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:47:04.000Z","msg":"推"}]}